content: linear: Focused on identifying and documenting a wide range of issues across the ElizaOS ecosystem, creating 12 issues, 7 of which were closed, covering topics from new CLI features (`elizaos/eliza#5573`) and documentation improvements (`elizaos/eliza#5638`) to critical CI test failures (`elizaos/eliza#5715`, `elizaos/eliza#5714`) and CLI command functionality.
